---
title: Cajun-Spiced Turkey & Mushroom Cavatappi with Creamy Tomato Sauce, Green Pepper & Scallions
description: Get ready for a rich, luscious vegan pasta dinner! Coconut milk may sound like an odd addition to your go-to red sauce, but trust us, it’s what gives our vegan veggie-packed pasta its next-level creaminess. You’ll start by sautéing mushrooms and green pepper, adding scallion and garlic, then creating a creamy spiced roux right in the pan for maximum Cajun flavor. Crushed tomatoes and coconut milk bring it all together for a sauce so delicious that cavatappi pasta can’t resist hopping right in. If you’re feeling the bayou in you, finish with hot sauce and let the good times roll!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6436fc670f64d25e8f0eda9f-2d4573a7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cajun-spiced-turkey-mushroom-cavatappi-6436fc670f64d25e8f0eda9f-fa7e04b8.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cajun-spiced-turkey-mushroom-cavatappi-6436fc670f64d25e8f0eda9f
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 990 kcal
  fat: 42 g
  saturated fat: 19 g
  carbohydrates: 104 g
  sugar: 23 g
